ARM.title: Arm Holdings Sees Q4 Adjusted Earnings Per Share $0.28 - $0.32
ARM.text: Feb 7 (Reuters) - Arm Holdings Plc O9TY.F::ARM HOLDINGS: QTRLY ADJUSTED EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.29 VERSUS LSEG IBES ESTIMATE $0.25.ARM HOLDINGS:  QTRLY TOTAL REVENUE $824 MILLION VERSUS LSEG IBES ESTIMATE $761.6 MILLION.ARM HOLDINGS: SEES Q4 ADJUSTED EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.28 - $0.32.ARM HOLDINGS: SEES Q4 REVENUE $850 MILLION - $900 MILLION.Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.21, REVENUE VIEW $780.3 MILLION -- LSEG IBES DATA.ARM HOLDINGS: SEES FY ADJUSTED EARNINGS PER SHARE $1.20 - $1.24.FY2024 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $1.07, REVENUE VIEW $3.05 BILLION -- LSEG IBES DATA.ARM HOLDINGS: EXPECT TO GET HIGHER ROYALTY RATES PER DEVICE AS PARTNERS DEPLOY MORE ARM TECHNOLOGY PER DEVICE COMBINED WITH ADVANCED ARM TECHNOLOGY.ARM HOLDINGS: 7.7 BILLION ARM-BASED CHIPS FOR SEPT QUARTER SHIPPING PERIOD, TAKING CUMULATIVE TOTAL TO OVER 280 BILLION.ARM HOLDINGS: SEES FY REVENUE $3.16 BILLION - $3.21 BILLION.Further company coverage: O9TY.F. ((Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com;)).
